My name is Mashal and I work in the business research division of CognitiveScale. 

Our Chief Product Officer, Nij Chawla will be visiting us on Jan 8th-11th in Hyderabad. He along with our GM, Pankaj Vaish and the Head of Technology & Products (India), Sridhar Seshadri would like to meet your team to discuss potential opportunities that could benefit us both.  

CognitiveScale is looking to build a boutique SI Partner ecosystem focused on AI. We have an emerging platform and an upcoming AI marketplace that we would like to talk through and explore mutually beneficial opportunities. This could be a nice win for both sides.

Just to give you a brief overview on who we are and what we do.

CognitiveScale is headquartered in Austin, Texas, and has offices in New York, London and Hyderabad. We have successfully deployed AI products in multiple Global 500 Companies, and have formed strategic go-to-market and technology partnerships with IBM, Microsoft, and Deloitte. Also, we got ranked #1 out of 1650 AI companies by CBInsights

CognitiveScale delivers industry-specific AI solutions for financial services, healthcare, and digital commerce markets that drive customer engagement and conversion, improve decision-making, and empower employees. The company’s AI platform and AI solutions help large enterprises increase user engagement, improve decision-making, and deliver self-learning and self-assuring business processes.

I was wondering if we could get some time on 10th of January, for around 90 minutes.

Please feel free to get back to me if you have questions.
